_sText: SURF _ TRON _ NJV ================== ### Inspired by the movie, I decided to create this map. It has a simple but tricky surf, with the movie's glowing colors on it. This is a non-jail version, perfect for timer surf servers. I was requested to do it, so here it is :D ### I hope yall like this map.
